subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Rubin, a 19-year-old from Long Island, defeated the 17th-seeded Paire, a Frenchman, by 7-6 (4), 7-6 (6), 7-6 (5) at the Australian Open.
